0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:618:"<p>edit: 12/27/12: Affiliate Manager is fixed and back online We&#8217;ve been working with our friends at 9Seeds on some bug reports regarding Affiliate Manager. &#8220;There is a problem with WP Affiliate Manager 1.4.x and earlier and WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x. We have determined what the issue and are currently working on a fix. The issue only [...]</p><p>The post <a href="http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-affiliate-manager-1-4-x-conflict-with-wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-x/">WP Affiliate Manager 1.4.x Conflict with WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x</a> appeared first on <a href="http://getshopped.org">GetShopped.org</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"amandablum";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2107:"<p><strong>edit: 12/27/12: Affiliate Manager is fixed and back online</strong></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve been working with our friends at 9Seeds on some bug reports regarding <a href="http://wpaffiliatemanager.com/forum/technical-support/issue-with-wp-affiliate-manager-and-wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-x/#p187">Affiliate Manager.</a></p>\n<p><em>&#8220;There is a problem with WP Affiliate Manager 1.4.x and earlier and WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x. We have determined what the issue and are currently working on a fix. The issue only presents itself on new installations, where you&#8217;re activating WP Affiliate Manager for the first time with WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x.</em></p>\n<p>People that have had WP e-Commerce 3.8.8.x (or earlier) and WP Affiliate Manager running together smoothly should not worry about the upgrade to WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x. The problem only occurs when WP Affiliate Manager is activated for the first time with WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x.</p>\n<p>If you have found this information before installing &amp; activating WP Affiliate Manager and WP e-Commerce for the first time, there is a workaround. Install and activate WP Affiliate Manager first, and then WP e-Commerce.</p>\n<p>We are currently working on version 1.5 to fix this, and expect that it will be released within the next two weeks. Since the bug renders WP Affiliate Manager in a state of partial installation, we&#8217;ve had to take extensive steps to make sure those existing partial installations will be repaired to full working order. Announcements regarding the release (and possible betas for those with partial installations) will be made here.&#8221;</p>\n<p>For our part here at WP e-Commerce and Getshopped, we&#8217;ve temporarily removed Affiliate Manager from the store while this issue is remedied. We&#8217;ll keep in touch here regarding updates.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-affiliate-manager-1-4-x-conflict-with-wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-x/">WP Affiliate Manager 1.4.x Conflict with WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x</a> appeared first on <a href="http://getshopped.org">GetShopped.org</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:106:"http://getshopped.org/getshopped-news/wp-affiliate-manager-1-4-x-conflict-with-wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-x/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:41:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 and Gold Cart 2.9.7.2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:87:"http://getshopped.org/wp-e-commerce-plugin/wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-3-and-gold-cart-2-9-7-2/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:96:"http://getshopped.org/wp-e-commerce-plugin/wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-3-and-gold-cart-2-9-7-2/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 27 Nov 2012 04:22:35 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:20:"WP e-Commerce Plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://getshopped.org/?p=295114";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:623:"<p>WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 and Gold Cart 2.9.7.2 are now available for download. WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 contains several important bug fixes and changes: * New: Add support for quantity field in default grid view template. * New: Let plugins add new column to product variation list table via filter ''wpsc_manage_product_variations_custom_column''. * Fix: Blank transaction results page [...]</p><p>The post <a href="http://getshopped.org/wp-e-commerce-plugin/wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-3-and-gold-cart-2-9-7-2/">WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 and Gold Cart 2.9.7.2</a> appeared first on <a href="http://getshopped.org">GetShopped.org</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"Gary Cao";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2663:"<p>WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 and Gold Cart 2.9.7.2 are now available for download.</p>\n<p>WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 contains several important bug fixes and changes:</p>\n<pre>* New: Add support for quantity field in default grid\r\n  view template.\r\n* New: Let plugins add new column to product variation list\r\n  table via filter ''wpsc_manage_product_variations_custom_column''.\r\n* Fix: Blank transaction results page when using paypal gateways.\r\n* Fix: Comment form is displayed even though comment is closed on\r\n  products page.\r\n* Fix: Fatal error in formatting.php for some sites.\r\n* Fix: New countries in 3.8.9 automatically added to target market\r\n  list.\r\n* Fix: PayPal Standard doesnt'' take care of coupons.\r\n* Fix: Punctuation in pending transaction email.</pre>\n<p>Gold Cart is now 100% compatible with WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.x series. All you need to do is upgrade to 2.7.9.2. The following issues have been addressed:</p>\n<pre>* Fix: Gold Cart gateways are not properly added.\r\n* Fix: Remove fixed 650px width for grid view.\r\n* Fix: Fatal error when WP e-Commerce is not activated\r\n  (especially during automatic upgrade).\r\n* Fix: PHP Notice in auth_net class.\r\n* Fix: Gold Cart display type is inconsistent at times.\r\n* Fix: Error with WPSC_Subscription.\r\n* Fix: 3.8.9 compatibility issues.\r\n* Fix: Make sure colorbox works.\r\n* Fix: Language text domain, and add Hungarian.</pre>\n<p>It is extremely important that before you upgrade to 3.8.9.3, please back up your files and databases. <a href="http://ithemes.com/member/go.php?r=27731&amp;i=l44">Backup Buddy</a> is our top choice for making backup simple and effortless.</p>\n<h5>How to upgrade</h5>\n<p>You can simply use WordPress automatic update feature to download and install WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.</p>\n<p>If that doesn&#8217;t work for you, try the following steps for a manual upgrade:</p>\n<p>- <a href="http://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-e-commerce.3.8.9.3.zip">Download WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 from here</a> and save it to your computer.</p>\n<p>- Extract the downloaded package to a folder on your computer.</p>\n<p>- Upload the contents of that folder to this path on your server, overwriting all existing files: <code>wp-content/plugins/wp-e-commerce</code></p>\n<p>As for Gold Cart update, you can get your new update files <a href="http://getshopped.org/extend/premium-upgrades-files/">here</a>, at which point you will need your API Key to release your download.</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://getshopped.org/wp-e-commerce-plugin/wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-3-and-gold-cart-2-9-7-2/">WP e-Commerce 3.8.9.3 and Gold Cart 2.9.7.2</a> appeared first on <a href="http://getshopped.org">GetShopped.org</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:92:"http://getshopped.org/wp-e-commerce-plugin/wp-e-commerce-3-8-9-3-and-gold-cart-2-9-7-2/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"32";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:53:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"Cyber Monday? Heck no-we’re 40% off *all week*";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";